guild.desc: Sends a chat message to guild members only across all servers.

squad.desc: Sends a chat message to squad only.

client_speed.desc: Sets the client time scale factor.

server_times.desc: Shows the total time players have spent in a server.

claim.desc: Claims daily streak rewards & stars drop buffs.

report.desc: Reports a user for chat toxicity.

unblock_all.desc: Unlocks all blocked users from chat.

gen_egg.desc: Generates egg reloads. petCount is how many mobs the egg should spawn. Power is a strength value given to the pet mob. If the power is very high, egg will have large reloads and vice-versa. MinUseTime is the minimum hatch time to increase the rarity of the spawned pet. If hatch time goes below that, rarity of the pet is increased. In simpler words, if the cutoff is large, eggs will very easily spawn high rarity pets.

petal_power.desc: Displays auto computed petal powers. Might not be accurate.

user_petal_purchases.desc: Lets you see total petals purchased by users.

lang.desc: Let's you set a custom lanuage file for the game. Not fully implementd.

give_all.desc: Gives all petals of a rarity.

run_on_join.desc: Runs the commands when you join as an admin. Separate by comma.

tickrate.desc: Sets server update rate. Default is 20 times per second.

petal_size.desc: Sets your petal size factor. Default is 1.

orbit.desc: Changes trajectory of your petal orbit. Do "/orbit reset" to revert back to circular orbit. Shape params are optional but you can pass them like "/orbit 3 5 18 18".

wall_thickness.desc: Defines wall edge thickness. Default is 12.

tp_all.desc: Teleports everyone to (x, y) in grid coordinates.

tp.desc: Teleports you to (x, y) in grid coordinates.

spawn.desc: Spawns mobs. Use underscore instead of spaces in mob names.

droprates.desc: Display droprates table for a petal rarity factor. Closer to 0 means more rare petal and vice-versa. Should be betwen 0 and 1.

give.desc: Puts petal in your inventory. Use underscore instead of spaces in petal names.

ygg.desc: Revives you if you are dead.

immune.desc: Makes your flower immune to any damage.

ghost.desc: Disables collision on your flower. Use the same command to toggle it back on.

fov.desc: Sets your field of view factor.
